metadata.name: The Hooded Man #1⚜️🥷🏽
metadata.description:
The hooded man’s journey begins here👣
This is the hooded man’s first created artwork 🖼. This shows him at the start of his journey which indicates that this piece is the Og to the entire collection and will be the only piece of artwork that holds these expressed traits. This art depicts the hooded man at the very beginning of his journey of trying to see the world for what it really is day by day and night after night🌃. You’ll see the hooded man grow and change numerous times throughout his journey in life💙will you be there to witness his journey?🍀
You ever wanted to figure out the actual meaning to life? You ever wanted to just know why?!???!?…….well…….this is why he’s going on this journey, to show people like you that no matter what he comes across you can get through it and go for what you want in this “Life” thing🔆
